import React from 'react'
import Hero from './hero/Hero'
import AboutCard from '../about/AboutCard'
import HAbout from './HAbout'

const Home = () => {
  return (
      <>
        <Hero />
        <HAbout />
        <AboutCard />
      </>    
  )
}

export default Home
